node.title: Search underway for swimmer missing in Canterbury's Waimakariri river
node.description: A police spokesperson says emergency services were called shortly after 7pm after a person jumped into the river but did not resurface.
node.content:
["An extensive search and rescue operation is underway for a missing swimmer in North Canterbury.", "", "
The Waimakariri river. Photo: Wikimedia Commons
", "A police spokesperson says emergency services were called shortly after 7pm after a person jumped into the Waimakariri river but did not resurface.", "Coastguard, surf lifesavers, a search and rescue helicopters and police are all involved."]
